Class SalesRepresentative

  • java.lang.Object
    • ro.siit.SalesRepresentative
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<SalesRepresentative>

    public class SalesRepresentative
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<SalesRepresentative>
    This class creates SalesRepresentative objects which have 4 properties You must pass in 3 parameters and then revenue is calculated automatically by multiplying sales and quota This class implements Comparable interface to be able to make a comparison between each sales person's revenue
